25 (11) Data processed or maintained in any of the following ways:
26 a. In the course of an individual applying to, employed by, or acting as
27 an agent or independent contractor of a controller, processor, or third
28 party, to the extent that the data is collected and used within the context
29 of that role.
30 b. As the emergency contact information of an individual, used for
31 emergency contact purposes.
32 c. Necessary to retain to administer benefits for another individual
33 relating to the individual who is the subject of the information under
34 sub-subdivision a. of this subdivision and used for the purposes of
